--- ---
---
---@param self Gio.TcpConnection # a `GTcpConnection`
---@param graceful_disconnect (boolean|nil) # Whether to do graceful disconnects or not
---@return nil
function Gio.TcpConnection:set_graceful_disconnect(graceful_disconnect) end

